ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectAppointment of the Honorable Karina Gould and the Honourable Ruby Sahota
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2024-75 of January 30, 2024; and (2) appointing the Honourable KARINA GOULD and the Honourable RUBY SAHOTA, members of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, to be members of the Board of Internal Economy of the House of Commons.
